These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
Movie-Genre: satire, martial-arts, comedy, horror
1. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1
2. Food:mango == Movie-Genre:horror##1
3. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the right of Movie-Genre:satire##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Movie-Genre:horror##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of Movie-Genre:satire##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | satire     | comedy   | horror |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
Flower: rose, azalea, tulip, dahlia
1. Hobby:woodworking == Flower:azalea##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of Flower:tulip##1
5. Flower:azalea is on the left of Flower:rose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Flower   | tulip    | azalea      | rose | dahlia |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
