Movie-Genre: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
2. City:san-francisco == Movie-Genre:crime##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of City:hannover##1
5. City:berlin is on the left of Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| City         | san-francisco | hannover | berlin   | colone |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

