3. Color:blue is on the left of Color:grey##1
4. Color:blue is on the right of Color:red##1
5. Sport:basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | red | blue | grey  | amber      |
