.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Nationality: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
Beverage: iced-tea, mirinda, tea, fanta
1. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1
2. Beverage:mirinda is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:mexican##1
4. Nationality:nigerian == Beverage:fanta##1
5. Beverage:iced-tea is on the left of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Beverage     | tea  | iced-tea    | mirinda       | fanta |

 